    "8 Prompt4/answer4 result from the offline bot version when answering a prompt, while the offline version is more straightforward.",
    "The offline version is suitable for extracting information readily available from the loaded factory data CSV file.Note -Assumption:• Our industrial bot results represent the backend thinking process that the I5.0 factory model should go through before initiating auto-parameter configuration and overtime production runs (after ascertaining workers' and environmental safety).",
    "• We assume that the remaining actions and technology needed to execute the automatic parameters configuration in the PLC and the SCADA system are performed as in the I4.0 model [53].",
